data.description: Open Family, Kitchen and Dining with split floor plan. Large Family room with gas log fireplace, crown molding, built-ins and lots of natural light all open to Kitchen with granite, stainless steel appliances including Fridge and Pantry, all open to Dining with large windows overlooking backyard. Entering from garage is a large Mudroom and Laundry Room. 3 Bedrooms with large closets, ceiling fans and bath. Large Primary Bedroom suite with ceiling fan, 2 walk-in closets, soaker tub and shower. Backyard is level with wood fence and no backyard neighbor. No Carpet! Chest Freezer & Washer/Dryer DO NOT CONVEY. Docs Online
